rd\">\n      <h3>Growth Support</h3>\n      <p>Helps reduce hair fall while supporting stronger, fuller-looking hair.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"elixara-card\">\n      <h3>For Thinning Hair</h3>\n      <p>Ideal for stress-related shedding, post-partum hair fall, weak roots, and thinning areas.</p>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.elixara-benefits{\n  display:grid;\n  grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);\n  gap:25px;\n  margin-top:50px;\n}\n\n.elixara-card{\n  background:#fff;\n  border-radius:28px;\n  padding:35px;\n  box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n  border-left:6px solid #2f6b46;\n}\n\n.elixara-card h3{\n  font-size:24px;\n  margin:0 0 15px;\n  color:#111;\n  font-weight:500;\n}\n\n.elixara-card p{\n  font-size:20px;\n  line-height:1.7;\n  color:#6d6d6d;\n  margin:0;\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width:768px){\n\n  .elixara-benefits{\n    display:flex;\n    overflow-x:auto;\n    gap:18px;\n    padding-bottom:12px;\n    scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-benefits > div{\n    min-width:85%;\n    scroll-snap-align:start;\n    flex-shrink:0;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-benefits::-webkit-scrollbar{\n    display:none;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-card{\n    padding:30px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-card h3{\n    font-size:23px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-card p{\n    font-size:18px;\n  }\n\n}\n</style>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top:-80px;\"></div>",
